Title: 1858 by Caymus Vineyards Cabernet Sauvignon Paso Robles
Body (HTML): Paso Robles, CA- From Caymus Vineyards. Black cherry and plum hit the front of the palate. Baking spice, with touches of vanilla and oak accompany the fruit while adding layers of complexity. Balanced with light acidity and fine tannins on the finish.
Tags: Cabernet Sauvignon, Red Wine, Central Coast, Paso Robles
